high_descs: Move to the towel ring to the left of the sink
Pick up the rag from the ring
Move to the bath tub behind you
Put the rag into the bath tub
Move to the towel ring to the right of the sink
Pick up the rag on the towel ring
Move to the bath tub behind you
Put the rag into the bath tub next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two clean rags into the bath tub from the towel rings.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight, then turn right to the area between the metal rack and the sink.
Take the towel from the towel ring on the wall.
Turn around, go to the bath tub where the black mat is.
Put the towel in the bath tub.
Turn around, go to the right of the sink.
Take the towel from the towel ring on the wall.
Turn around, go to the bath tub where the black mat is.
Put the towel in the bath tub to the right of the other towel.
anns.task_desc: Put towels in the bath tub.

high_descs: Move across the room to the towel rack hanging on the left side of the mirror.
Take the towel off the towel rack on the wall.
Turn around and move across the room to the bath tub.
Place the towel in the bath tub.
Move across the room to the towel rack hanging on the right side of the mirror.
Take the towel off the towel rack on the wall.
Turn around and move across the room to the bath tub.
Place the towel in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Gather towels to place in bath tub for later use.
